msg":"點解唔搵d大規模d既做?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:59:44.000Z","msg":"當初搵工就正正係兩間offer，除左而家哩間，另一間係連鎖經營的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但一黎打左幾年工，唔知係我天真定一直都係好好彩遇到貴人，覺得細公司既老闆會有人情味啲同埋&ldquo;易跑出&rdquo;啲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">二黎我職業係多數都有target有份committion分，咁我最後就揀左佔地比較大既而家哩間公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"72a891b985ee91010f7ac76b8270b60b70921631","tid":565525,"uid":31990,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T07:49:40.000Z","msg":"我老闆<br />\n<br />\n無雙糧無花紅<br />\n<br />\n團年飯抽現金獎($1000~$200) 大獎到安慰獎<br />\n<br />\n自己都有份抽<br />\n<br />\n抽左$800,然後話自己都係公司員工,抽到真係好開心,可以過肥年,跟住袋左落手袋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6794d5bc7c7d85cb52366fb23c8d1b53f35bbf97","tid":565525,"uid":44061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T07:54:53.000Z","msg":"點解新年放假要扣錢? 初一二三唔係法定假黎架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266e872228b68f8ad3bd9cdebb710d4daccd7fa6","tid":565525,"uid":39673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72a891b985ee91010f7ac76b8270b60b70921631","tid":565525,"uid":31990,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T07:49:40.000Z","msg":"我老闆<br />\n<br />\n無雙糧無花紅<br />\n<br />\n團年飯抽現金獎($1000~$200) 大獎到安慰獎<br />\n<br />\n自己都有份抽<br />\n<br />\n抽左$800,然後話自己都係公司員工,抽到真係好開心,可以過肥年,跟住袋左落手袋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T07:57:50.000Z","msg":"so cheap <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後巴打抽幾多"},{"pid":"0386ff61a7aa3f064c09542f7eb78d7a53da4452","tid":565525,"uid":39673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6794d5bc7c7d85cb52366fb23c8d1b53f35bbf97","tid":565525,"uid":44061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T07